meta.testSetDescription:
Set contains a total of ~1400 images from the BRCA TCGA collection, I have only included
    DX1 slides; the data set is split into 75/20/5 training/testing/validation
    By Default, it will assume a 256x256 padded thumbnail image output although you can change this if you want
    in the download script
    This will ONLY be downloading a single class of images i.e. BRCA
